<p><strong><em>Nimble Escape.</em></strong> The goblin can take the Disengage or Hide action as a bonus action on each of its turns.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Scimitar.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 5 (1d6 + 2) slashing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Shortbow.</em></strong> Ranged Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. Hit: 5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.</p>

